{
  "format_notes": "getDataPacket(payload, cmd, pkgSize) chunks `payload` into pieces of at most pkgSize bytes and frames each chunk. Each case gives cmd, pkg_size, input_hex (lowercase contiguous hex of the full payload before chunking), and output_hex_chunks: a JSON array of lowercase hex strings, one per chunk, each being the *complete framed frame* for that chunk (01 + escape(len2BE + cmd + 00 + len4BE(total payload size) + idx2BE + chunkLen2BE + chunk bytes + 1-byte XOR checksum) + 03). Chunk order in the array matches chunk index order (0, 1, 2, ...).",
